2013年发布了第二版的《一觸即發》扩充。<ref name="z5y">{{Cite web|title=5 years of Pandemic: the virus is growing stronger!|url=http://zmangames.com/nouvelles-details.php?id=286|accessdate=2013-09-25|date=2013-01-14|publisher=[[Z-Man_Games|Z-Man Games]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914041337/http://zmangames.com/nouvelles-details.php?id=286|archivedate=September 14, 2013}}</ref> 

