-14 |archive-date=2021-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210731182425/https://boardgametheories.com/best-pandemic-expansions-and-versions/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[https://boardgamesland.com/ Board Games Land] {{Wayback|url=https://boardgamesland.com/ |date=20210422004757 }}将该游戏描述为“智能，戏剧性和主题性的游戏，旨在创造只有少数几款棋盘游戏才能达到的令人难忘的时刻，充满情感的高潮和低谷”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Best Legacy Board Games of 2019 (Updated Mar. 19) - Top 10 Review|url=https://boardgamesland.com/best-legacy-board-games/|accessdate=2019-03-28|date=2019-03-27|work=Board Games Land|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128133337/https://boardgamesland.com/best-legacy-board-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

